Package com.github.wuic.engine.impl.embedded

This package contains the engines which don't delegate its work to any library like YUI Compressor.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AbstractCacheEngine This class is an abstraction of an engine which reads from a cache the nuts associated to a workflow to be processed.
CGAbstractCompressorEngine This engine defines the base treatments to execute when compressing a set of files.
CGAbstractSpriteProvider Abstraction of the implementation of what is a SpriteProvider.
CGBinPacker<T> This packer is inspired from the grower bin packing algorithm explained by Jakes Gordon to give a position to a set of dimensions in the lowest area.
CGCssBackgroundUrlLineInspector This class inspects CSS files to extract nuts referenced as a background URL to process it.
CGCssImportLineInspector This class inspects CSS files to extract nuts referenced with @import statement to process it.
CGCssInspectorEngine This engines parses CSS files thanks to a CGCssImportLineInspector and a CGCssBackgroundUrlLineInspector.
CGCssSpriteProvider This SpriteProvider generates CSS code to represent the sprites.
CGImageAggregatorEngine This engine is in charge to merge images into one final image.
CGImageCompressorEngine Engine that compress images.
CGJavascriptSpriteProvider This class provides sprite throughout javascript language.
CGTextAggregatorEngine This engine can aggregate all the specified files in one path.
CGTextInspectorEngine Basic inspector engine for text nuts processing text line per line.
MemoryMapCacheEngine This engine reads from a Map kept in memory the nuts associated to a workflow to be processed.
ScheduledCacheEngine This abstract engine is able to clear its cache in a particular interleave.
 

Package com.github.wuic.engine.impl.embedded Description

This package contains the engines which don't delegate its work to any library like YUI Compressor.
